    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, while the transmission shifts through all gears without any hesitation. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, though you may notice some light wear on the driver's seat bolster consistent with regular use. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, although there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper. Overall, this is a solid, dependable car that is ready to be driven home today.",
